    • 构造器详细资料

      • PipelineAggregationSpec

        public PipelineAggregationSpec(ParseField name,
                               Writeable.Reader<? extends PipelineAggregationBuilder> builderReader,
                               Writeable.Reader<? extends PipelineAggregator> aggregatorReader,
                               PipelineAggregator.Parser parser)
        Specification of a PipelineAggregator.
        参数:
        name - holds the names by which this aggregation might be parsed. The ParseField.getPreferredName() is special as it is the name by under which the readers are registered. So it is the name that the PipelineAggregationBuilder and PipelineAggregator should return from NamedWriteable.getWriteableName().
        builderReader - the reader registered for this aggregation's builder. Typically a reference to a constructor that takes a StreamInput
        aggregatorReader - reads the PipelineAggregator from a stream
        parser - reads the aggregation builder from XContent

      • PipelineAggregationSpec

        public PipelineAggregationSpec(java.lang.String name,
                               Writeable.Reader<? extends PipelineAggregationBuilder> builderReader,
                               Writeable.Reader<? extends PipelineAggregator> aggregatorReader,
                               PipelineAggregator.Parser parser)
        Specification of a PipelineAggregator.
        参数:
        name - name by which this aggregation might be parsed or deserialized. Make sure it is the name that the PipelineAggregationBuilder and PipelineAggregator should return from NamedWriteable.getWriteableName().
        builderReader - the reader registered for this aggregation's builder. Typically a reference to a constructor that takes a StreamInput
        aggregatorReader - reads the PipelineAggregator from a stream
        parser - reads the aggregation builder from XContent
